son but demand the ransom anyway.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":3.1084,"vote_count":1084,"poster_path":"/tgNjemQPG96uIezpiUiXFcer5ga.jpg","release_date":"1963-03-01","vote_average":8.347,"backdrop_path":"/A62quSOB8otoZvGiLvMVZ9G4BiO.jpg","original_title":"天国と地獄","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12496,"adult":false,"title":"The Twilight Samurai","video":false,"overview":"Seibei Iguchi leads a difficult life as a low ranking samurai at the turn of the nineteenth century. A widower with a meager income, Seibei struggles to take care of his two daughters and senile mother. New prospects seem to open up when the beautiful Tomoe, a childhood friend, comes back into he and his daughters' life, but as the Japanese feudal system unravels, Seibei is still bound by the code of honor of the samurai and by his own sense of social precedence. How can he find a way to do what is best for those he loves?","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":1.1878,"vote_count":348,"poster_path":"/bB2M8UF8wc9flfGWkcgkTTf8Mzr.jpg","release_date":"2002-11-02","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/pNpQf1ZwdKLHo25jFSDisMfqXJl.jpg","original_title":"たそがれ清兵衛","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12500,"adult":false,"title":"American Ninja","video":false,"overview":"Joe Armstrong, an orphaned drifter with little respect for much other than martial arts, finds himself on an American Army base in The Philippines after a judge gives him a choice of enlistment or prison. On one of his first missions driving a convoy, his platoon is attacked by a group of rebels who try to steal the weapons the platoon is transporting and kidnap the base colonel's daughter.","genre_ids":[28],"popularity":1.6256,"vote_count":471,"poster_path":"/oH8eKi4Bt50tyXQIsYaM2KJqXd3.jpg","release_date":"1985-08-30","vote_average":5.983,"backdrop_path":"/7zY3QYzr2eZs2YNbEB0JObH7A9O.jpg","original_title":"American Ninja","original_language":"en"},{"id":12504,"adult":false,"title":"The Outsider","video":false,"overview":"Philippe Jordan is a policeman prone to advancing the cause of justice by any means necessary. On his agenda is a powerful drug cartel working out of Paris and Marseilles, with a drug lord who is essentially inaccessible -- but not immortal.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"popularity":1.0107,"vote_count":217,"poster_path":"/li1IrkJldDlHNm8DtcA79b251fS.jpg","release_date":"1983-10-26","vote_average":6.813,"backdrop_path":"/roLOinUoMpksR4D7Cmz7oQPaTwC.jpg","original_title":"Le Marginal","original_language":"fr"},{"id":12520,"adult":false,"title":"The Last Supper","video":false,"overview":"A group of idealistic but frustrated liberals succumb to the temptation of murdering right-wing pundits for their political beliefs.","genre_ids":[35,53,80,18],"popularity":0.9243,"vote_count":296,"poster_path":"/oIgPiiM0qD1mCo1SYG3Sd0vmKTa.jpg","release_date":"1995-09-08","vote_average":6.515,"backdrop_path":"/3yLMuH0Xp5gp7Wls3LfcVn6lVU9.jpg","original_title":"The Last Supper","original_language":"en"},{"id":12524,"adult":false,"title":"Titus","video":false,"overview":"Titus Andronicus returns from the wars and sees his sons and daughters taken from him, one by one. Shakespeare's goriest and earliest tragedy.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":3.3941,"vote_count":282,"poster_path":"/82mCeQoeT2C7h7vR6Ot9MQotE1R.jpg","release_date":"1999-12-25","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/xwlShstQ7tODGkJJQ2ddM2JoNMu.jpg","original_title":"Titus","original_language":"en"},{"id":12528,"adult":false,"title":"Southern Comfort","video":false,"overview":"A squad of National Guards on an isolated weekend exercise in the Louisiana swamp must fight for their lives when they anger local Cajuns by stealing their canoes. Without live ammunition and in a strange country, their experience begins to mirror the Vietnam experience.","genre_ids":[53,28],"popularity":1.2765,"vote_count":339,"poster_path":"/nBPOcxiqc0PsG7Hz58JxSUN5BF0.jpg","release_date":"1981-09-24","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/1pXco8EiCGtYyBZuNSQIu6980lf.jpg","original_title":"Southern Comfort","original_language":"en"},{"id":12532,"adult":false,"title":"Rottweiler","video":false,"overview":"Dante travels across a desolate, futuristic Spain in search of his girlfriend, Ula. He is pursued by a bloodthirsty, cybernetic Rottweiler.","genre_ids":[27,878,28],"popularity":0.5028,"vote_count":64,"poster_path":"/uONkXsdAU11mTC8Z6SeJQyuLptC.jpg","release_date":"2004-12-01","vote_average":3.336,"backdrop_path":"/kqbvDnt9V3tZljvefUn5NQrTlad.jpg","original_title":"Rottweiler","original_language":"en"},{"id":12539,"adult":false,"title":"The Black Tulip","video":false,"overview":"Aristocrat Guillaume de Saint Preux leads a double life as a masked bandit known as the Black Tulip. The Black Tulip only robs rich aristocrats, so the local peasants regard him as a hero. Baron La Mouche is convinced Guillaume is the Tulip. During a robbery, he scars the Tulip's face, and hopes to use this to expose Guillaume, but Guillaume is one step ahead.","genre_ids":[12],"popularity":0.9848,"vote_count":139,"poster_path":"/fYaIoQrEEz2fnJcY3KAzBsPwvF4.jpg","release_date":"1964-02-28","vote_average":6.281,"backdrop_path":"/vA3lzpeZXZ80XtcxE8213YQUJut.jpg","original_title":"La Tulipe noire","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1069409,"adult":false,"title":"Wakanohana: The Story of the Devil of the Dohyō","video":false,"overview":"A film about sumo wrestler Wakanohana Kanji I. He was nicknamed \"Devil of the dohyo\" due to his excellent fighting spirit and endurance.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2904,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/dX5ag4y7pAQH6Pw5jENpFAMRDxB.jpg","release_date":"1956-12-27","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Wakanohana monogatari dohyou no oni","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12613,"adult":false,"title":"Street Fighter II: The Animated Movie","video":false,"overview":"Bison, the ruthless leader of the international terrorist organization Shadowlaw, has been desperately searching for the greatest fighter on the planet for years. He finds it in Ryu, a young wanderer who never stays in one place long enough for Bison to find him. He does, however, get a fix on Ken Masters, an American martial arts champion who studied with Ryu as a child under the same master. Meanwhile, Major Guile of the United States Army is forced to team up with Chun Li from China in hopes of apprehending Bison and putting a stop his international ring of crime.","genre_ids":[16,28],"popularity":1.2897,"vote_count":305,"poster_path":"/dZ1rqmE4eIhPbUCr7sn2Pw2wwGW.jpg","release_date":"1994-08-06","vote_average":7.052,"backdrop_path":"/reMt35KtqTTIy0mhcKA1PfuruDq.jpg","original_title":"ストリートファイター II MOVIE","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12618,"adult":false,"title":"Random Hearts","video":false,"overview":"After losing their spouses in a plane crash, an internal affairs cop and a congresswoman find each other's keys in each other's loved ones' possessions and discover that the two were having an affair.","genre_ids":[18,10749,53],"popularity":2.4843,"vote_count":413,"poster_path":"/k7LoKDWDesvYD7DXDh9Ewlxtcx8.jpg","release_date":"1999-10-08","vote_average":5.558,"backdrop_path":"/onOF95lPTacI4lKHGG9REPw3fHJ.jpg","original_title":"Random Hearts","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt11809034","twitter_id":"ruroken_movie","facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q103820244","instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":"ruroken_movie","facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":118166,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"BR","release_dates":[{"note":"Netflix","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2021-06-18T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"14"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2021-06-18T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"16"}]},{"iso_316